nodes.text: TD-4445 was a male who served in the sandtrooper division of the Stormtrooper Corps, in the Galactic Empire's army and served as the commander of a Dewback trooper squad around 0 BBY. He was stationed at Mos Eisley, Tatooine, and called for reinforcements when he and his unit engaged in a firefight with the crew of the Millennium Falcon as they escaped the city.
